<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is this a replacement for medical care?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely not. The Heart Health Method complements your medical care. We encourage you to work with your healthcare provider and many of our members share their progress with their doctors. Never stop or change medications without consulting your physician.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long until I see results?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Most members report feeling better within the first 2-3 weeks—increased energy, better sleep, improved digestion. Measurable improvements in blood pressure and cholesterol typically appear within 60-90 days of consistent application.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do I need to follow a strict diet?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">No extreme diets here. Our approach focuses on adding heart-healthy foods rather than restriction. You'll learn which foods support cardiovascular health and how to incorporate them deliciously into your existing preferences.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is this evidence-based?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. Every recommendation is grounded in peer-reviewed research from leading institutions. We cite our sources and stay current with the latest cardiovascular science. No fad diets or unproven supplements.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if I have specific dietary restrictions?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Our protocols are customizable for various dietary needs including vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and food allergies. The core principles adapt to your preferences while delivering the same cardiovascular benefits.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How much time does this require?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">The daily protocol takes about 10-15 minutes. Meal prep is designed to be efficient—most members spend 2 hours on Sunday preparing for the week. We focus on sustainable habits, not time-consuming routines.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
